data.description: Short Sale. Looking for a 3 bed, 2 bath block home to make your own? This house is located just 2 miles from Downtown Sanford & Riverwalk Park! Recent updates/upgrades include a new roof, new solar panels, new digital water heater powered by solar, new electrical panel, and new septic will be installed soon. This home has wood laminate flooring in the kitchen, tile in bathrooms, and carpet in the living room & bedrooms. The home also features a spacious fenced-in back yard with a 10x12 shop with electric available.
